Download xampp 
connect to server (start apache and MySQL)
open phpmyadmin by click on admin or typing localhost/phpmyadmin on browser
put code files in xampp-htdots 
create new database and give the database name same as in php code database name
and server name is localhost and username is root
then create table by adding no. of columns as you want
after that 
establish connection form the database

then open the webpage on browser by typing localhost/folder_name_saved_in_xampp-htdots
fill your form and submit and then refresh the database page after that you can see your data.
